{"tid":219995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(片)Google資助研發飛天車年底開售,司機不需持有飛行執照","createTime":"2017-04-27T15:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T03:37:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a00772e4d296f5dc3731f7eb9bbc05d85739eb5","tid":219995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=218948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D218948&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=2d178906\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D218948&h=c8a7e961\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=218948</a><br />\n2017年4月25日 14:46<br />\n【Now新聞台】飛天車不再只是科幻情節，Google資助研發的飛天車成功在美國試飛，預計年底前開售。司機不需持有飛行執照，人人也可達成飛天夢。<br />\n<br />\n飛天車經常在科幻電影出現，駕車在空中奔馳穿梭，在現實世界中亦快將實現。<br />\n<br />\n這輛飛天車可能與大家想像或電影中的很不同，與其說是一輛車，它更似現在時興的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n八個螺旋槳由電池驅動，重220磅，「開篷」的設計，司機坐在上面控制，有點像水上電單車。<br />\n<br />\n兩名有份設計的工程師親身在三藩市試駕，在離湖面約四半米「水上飄」，加減速、轉向均控制自如，飛天車能垂直升降，不用跑道，「泊車」很方便。<br />\n<br />\n飛天車已獲聯邦航空局批准在非繁忙地區飛行，被列為超輕型飛機類別，即是機師毋須持有飛行執照。<br />\n<br />\n研發的始創公司、由Google資助的Kitty Hawk預計，飛天車在年底前開售，未有定價。公司強調，產品的外表最終會跟這輛原型不同，亦會靜很多。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle創辦人佩奇表示，人人都有飛天夢，他很期望很快有一天能駕駛這輛飛天車升空。<br />\n<br />\n飛天夢並非Google獨有，多間科技公司正積極研發飛天車，包括空中巴士、Uber等。<br />\n<br />\n斯洛伐克公司AeroMobil這輛可由汽車變至成飛機的飛天車索價百多萬歐元，阿聯酋迪拜政府亦將於七月推出全球首輛無人駕駛的飛行的士。<br />\n<br />\n不過要開發天空仍挑戰重重，既要重新制訂空中交通法規，又要解決飛天車的安全和嘈音等問題，電池技術亦有待改良，才有足夠能源飛行合理距離。"},{"pid":"6916f785d468c69de90e7c6213e7f52eb7d3ccde","tid":219995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5624441d4cc47e283ce6609ccc0cc8354d498fbe","tid":219995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5777ac8dc0143a948d42e953fcf67d7adf3f6a","tid":219995,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:57:32.000Z","msg":"段片聽到now 講迪拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db5033c64baa8715d35527b408adca685d20010","tid":219995,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T22:19:46.000Z","msg":"血滴子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8dbee4808dfd09d7f3826189657c4a4d7acf56","tid":219995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56adeb9a807ac740e879e18f108ede12e06987d5","tid":219995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8865c99545ec3ee548411b13fc1418e2b5ca8482","tid":219995,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"Back to the future"}]}